steps.name: When  Get All users with Valid Endpoint and basic auth
Then  The response is status code as 200 and status line OK
When  Get All users with Invalid Endpoint and basic auth
Then  The response is status code as 404 and status line Not Found
When  Get All users with empty Endpoint and basic auth
Then  The response is status code as 404 and status line Not Found
When  Get All users with null Endpoint and basic auth
Then  The response is status code as 404 and status line Not Found
When  Get All users without auth
Then  The response is status code as 200 and status line OK
